{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3a65e0913e","title":"中央关于县区乡三级暂不进行三反和五反的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"573388e478","index":0,"year":1952,"month":2,"day":24,"articleId":"3a65e0913e"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji31","name":"毛泽东全集第31卷","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/31-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji31":{"comments":[{"id":"6e18dc05a8","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"3a65e0913e","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指1952年2月15日中共中央关于五反中对各类资本家的处理意见的指示。"}],"contents":[{"id":"526728e3d0","type":"title","text":"中央关于县区乡三级暂不进行三反和五反的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"3a65e0913e"},{"id":"6e18dc05a8","type":"paragraph","text":"各中央局，并转分局，省市区党委，地委：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"3a65e0913e"},{"id":"910db1a580","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）县区乡三级的三反，除省委地委为了典型试验之目的，可以个别地进行以外，一律待春耕完成以后再做，以免引起混乱，此点前已通知。（二）县区乡某些违法资本家中的五反，自前一律不要进行。已进行者，一律停止。将来何时进行及如何进行，中央将根据情况另行通知。（三）中等城市例如四平街、营口、石家庄、新乡、苏州、宁波、宜昌、衡州、江门、梧州、宝鸡、汉中、自流井、遵义等的违法资本家中何时进行五反及如何进行五反，须由各中央局、分局、省委区党委根据中央二月十五日指示则严格审查控制，逐一批准，以免混乱。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"3a65e0913e"},{"id":"bfcc3704db","type":"paragraph","text":"中央","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"3a65e0913e"},{"id":"5132648722","type":"paragraph","text":"二月二十四日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"3a65e0913e"}],"page":{"id":"829237bc43","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"3a65e0913e","start":436,"end":436}}}},"__N_SSG":true}